channel.title: Error Message help
channel.description:
Ok heres the story, I am using basic mopar and I amlearning the basics before eventually progressing into making my own server and all, I have mopar on my comp but the modems fried so it cant get on. My mom went and got a new laptop computer and I try to get on and it give me an error message saying
>>Java Virtual Machine Launcher<< X Could Not Find main class. Program will exit.
Pic:[IMG]http://i184.photobucket.com/albums/x209/Scythexp/errormsg.png[/img]
Now im pretty smart when it comes to computers but this has me baffeled could someone please explain whats happening and tell me how to fix it please.
